WEBVTT

1
01:58:03.830 --> 01:58:04.930 
明白了吗
Do you understand?

2
01:58:05.500 --> 01:58:08.960 
我们空降后  控制空降区让蓝队撤离
We drop in, clear LZs for Blue Team evacuation.

3
01:58:08.960 --> 01:58:10.760 
我们进入城市
We make our way into the city proper.

4
01:58:10.760 --> 01:58:12.430 
这些都是废弃建筑
These buildings are abandoned,

5
01:58:12.430 --> 01:58:14.890 
但我们得知  这里也有一道旋转门
but we learned there is a turnstile.

6
01:58:14.890 --> 01:58:17.350 
可能会遭到双向时间反击
Expect a bitemporal response.

7
01:58:17.350 --> 01:58:18.850 
他们有逆时间武器吗
They'll have inverse ordnance?

8
01:58:18.850 --> 01:58:21.020 
逆时间的  常规的
Inverse, conventional,

9
01:58:21.100 --> 01:58:24.230 
正向对手  逆向对手  他们都有
forward antagonists, inverted antagonists, they have it all.

10
01:58:24.360 --> 01:58:25.690 
在城市的另一边
On the other side of the city,

11
01:58:25.690 --> 01:58:28.570 
沿着山坡爬上去可以到达爆炸源
the ground rises to the ridge above the hypocenter.

12
01:58:28.570 --> 01:58:31.740 
小分队将从市区走这条通道
A splinter unit will take this tunnel from the city

13
01:58:31.990 --> 01:58:33.910 
到达山洞里的爆炸源
to the floor of the hypocenter.

14
01:58:33.910 --> 01:58:36.660 
蓝队在这里发现了一个入口
Blue Team located an entrance here.

